<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 12:30:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>香港民主活动人士黎智英否认在审判中煽动对中国的仇恨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-democracy-activist-jimmy-lai-denies-inciting-hatred-towards-china-2024-11-21/</link><description>民主活动人士黎智英周四在具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中作证的第二天表示，他反对暴力，并没有通过呼吁抗议来捍卫基本权利来煽动对中国和香港当局的仇恨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 12:24:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-democracy-activist-jimmy-lai-denies-inciting-hatred-towards-china-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国信托星公司融资10亿美元，收购麦当劳中国股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</link><description>两位知情人士称，Trusstar Capital 已为一只持续基金筹集了 10 亿美元，该基金将持有这家中国私募股权公司在麦当劳中国大陆和香港业务中的控股权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-trustar-raises-1-bln-vehicle-that-holds-mcdonalds-china-stake-sources-say-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达预计将实现三位数增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 11:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>在对特朗普关税的担忧之际，中国宣布促进贸易的政策措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-policy-measures-boost-trade-amid-worries-over-trump-tariffs-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国商务部周四宣布了一系列旨在促进中国对外贸易的政策措施，包括承诺加强对企业的融资支持和扩大农产品出口。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-policy-measures-boost-trade-amid-worries-over-trump-tariffs-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴联合电子商务部门应对日益激烈的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-integrate-e-commerce-platforms-into-one-business-group-2024-11-21/</link><description>阿里巴巴集团周四在一份证券交易所文件中表示，该公司将首次将其国内和国际电子商务平台整合为一个由一位领导者运营的单一业务部门。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 10:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-integrate-e-commerce-platforms-into-one-business-group-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称被监禁的前中国高官薄熙来之子正在探望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-son-jailed-former-senior-chinese-official-bo-xilai-is-visiting-2024-11-21/</link><description>台湾政府周四表示，被监禁的中国前高级领导人薄熙来的儿子在与一名台湾公民结婚后，出于个人原因访问台湾，这对于与中国政治精英有联系的人来说是罕见的旅行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-son-jailed-former-senior-chinese-official-bo-xilai-is-visiting-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国派遣特遣部队支持菲律宾驻南海部队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-backs-philippine-forces-south-china-sea-with-task-force-2024-11-21/</link><description>美国大使馆官员周四表示，美国军方正在通过特别工作组支持菲律宾在南海的行动，马尼拉称这一举措涉及情报、监视和侦察。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-backs-philippine-forces-south-china-sea-with-task-force-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国百度第三季度收入下降3%，符合市场预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-posts-3-fall-third-quarter-revenue-beats-market-estimates-2024-11-21/</link><description>百度周四公布第三季度收入下降 3%，符合市场预期，这家中国最大的互联网搜索提供商在经济低迷的情况下努力应对广告服务支出疲软的问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-posts-3-fall-third-quarter-revenue-beats-market-estimates-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾特使表示，对乌克兰的军事帮助“太敏感”，但代表处是一个目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/military-help-ukraine-too-sensitive-rep-office-goal-taiwan-envoy-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>台湾外交部副部长吴弗朗索瓦表示，台湾没有参与对乌克兰的军事援助，因为它“太敏感”，但希望在该国设立代表处。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:48:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/military-help-ukraine-too-sensitive-rep-office-goal-taiwan-envoy-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>德国10月破产率同比增长22.9%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/insolvencies-germany-up-229-year-on-year-october-2024-11-21/</link><description>德国统计局周四表示，德国 10 月份破产企业数量比去年同期增加了 22.9%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/insolvencies-germany-up-229-year-on-year-october-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国在湖南发现价值830亿美元的黄金储备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-finds-83-billion-worth-gold-reserves-hunan-2024-11-21/</link><description>据官方媒体新华社周四报道，中国在中部湖南省发现了价值 6000 亿元人民币（合 829 亿美元）的黄金储备。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-finds-83-billion-worth-gold-reserves-hunan-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中方愿就潜艇基础设施安全保持沟通</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-maintain-communication-submarine-infrastructure-security-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国外交部周四表示，中方愿与有关各方保持沟通，共同维护国际潜艇基础设施的安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 07:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-maintain-communication-submarine-infrastructure-security-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在全球峰会上推动外交努力，为特朗普关税做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bracing-trump-tariffs-chinas-xi-makes-diplomatic-push-global-summits-2024-11-21/</link><description>在唐纳德·特朗普连任美国领导人以来的首次全球会议上，中国国家主席习近平发起了外交攻势，对冲预期的新关税，并准备利用华盛顿与其盟友之间未来潜在的分歧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 07:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bracing-trump-tariffs-chinas-xi-makes-diplomatic-push-global-summits-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国资金枯竭，柬埔寨旗舰运河陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodias-flagship-canal-hot-water-china-funding-dries-up-2024-11-21/</link><description>在八月的一次仪式上，柬埔寨领导人洪马内跪下接受身穿藏红花长袍的僧侣的祝福，烟花和气球预示着一条运河的破土动工，他希望这条运河能够改变柬埔寨的经济命运。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:10:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodias-flagship-canal-hot-water-china-funding-dries-up-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>星巴克考虑与中国业务建立战略合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-considers-selling-stake-chinese-business-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-11-21/</link><description>星巴克周四重申，正在为其中国业务探索战略合作伙伴关系，此前有媒体报道称该公司正在考虑将业务股份出售给当地合作伙伴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-considers-selling-stake-chinese-business-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-11-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>